Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm David — a U.S. entrepreneur\Nwho's grown multiple brands from zero to\Nscale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to walk you through the\Nfastest way I know to run marketing on\Nautopilot: Pzhisen at pzhisen.online.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting started is incredibly simple,\Nfast, and convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You open the site, share your business idea, and\Ndeploy your AI employee team in minutes — no\Ncomplicated setup, no credit card required to\Nbegin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once your agents are live, they work for you\Ntwenty-four hours a day, seven days a week,\Nthree hundred sixty-five days a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They never sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They never take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They never clock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With Pzhisen, specialized AI agents\Nautomatically create promotional marketing\Ntweets and social copy for your brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They produce promotional marketing\Nvideos ready for distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They write promotional marketing emails\Nand send them to mainstream inboxes\Nworldwide — Gmail, Outlook, and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically reply to customer\Nservice messages, so your clients always\Nget help — day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They automatically analyze your market\Ncompetitiveness, your sales data, and\Nreal-time market conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They research industry trends and help\Nyou understand where the world's major\Nsectors are heading next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they publish for you across the world's\Nbiggest platforms: YouTube, TikTok, X, Facebook,\NWeChat Channels, Douyin, Tencent Video,\NKuaishou, Xiaohongshu — and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you have a personal website or a full\Nenterprise site, Pzhisen helps anyone, anywhere,\Npromote and grow online — fully automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's the result that matters most: Pzhisen has\Nalready helped thousands of individuals and businesses\Nworldwide generate one million dollars in revenue in a\Nsingle month through AI-powered promotion and marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're ready to put an AI team to\Nwork while you sleep, go to\Npzhisen.online — and start tonight.
